---
title: Steak and Horseradish Cheese Sauce with Parmesan Roasted Potatoes and Broccoli
description: Steak and horseradish were born to be together! We won't be surprised if you want to drench your plate in the accompanying creamy cheese sauce, which softens the pepperiness of the horseradish.
